-- Pearl ups stake in Resolution to 24.2 percent
-- 
-- Fri Oct 26, 2007 9:13am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/26/us-resolution-standard-life-stake-idUSWLA196420071026

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - British insurer Pearl has raised its stake in takeover target Resolution ( RSL.L ) to 24.2 percent, from 22.2 percent announced earlier on Friday. 

 Earlier on Friday, Pearl announced it had raised its bid for Resolution to 720p-per-share in cash, muscling in on Resolution's agreed takeover by another competitor, Standard Life ( SL.L ).